review_blob: 50 cl. bottle. Malt, grass and hops. A good balanced bitterness. Very light carbonated, the beer went flat in a few minutes.

Bottle from Super Brugsen. Flower, hops and citrusaroma. Appealing color and texture, but the taste of the IPA is way to "watered out" for my taste. A good choice if regular IPAs are to bitter and hoppy for your taste.
